Basic tests of the installation, checking accuracy and
convergence. Results of oconvergence tests are output as refinement
data and L_\infty norm of error, calculated as difference between
exact and computed solution for internal point source excitation (see
test-errors for format).

test-all:    convergence tests for GMSH geometries in ../Geometries

sphere-test: convergence test for hard sphere, using BEM3D native
	     spherical geometry generator

